
Parece que comenzaste a compartir el código HTML y CSS para una plantilla de factura. Aquí tienes un ejemplo completo y funcional a partir del código que comenzaste. Esto incluye el resto de la estructura y algunos estilos para que puedas ver cómo se presenta la factura en su totalidad.
Código HTML Completo para la Factura
html
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Factura ColproMarket #<%= invoice._id %><style>
:root {
--one-color: #FBFBFB;
--two-color: #E8F9FF;
--three-color: #C4D9FF;
--four-color: #C5BAFF;
--cambio: #8E7DBE;
--six-color: #cdcbfc;
--seven-color: #3813f0;
--text-primary: #333;
--text-secondary: #666;
--background: #f9f9f9;
--card-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
--border-color: #eee;
--header-bg: #1a2a6c;
--header-bg-gradient: linear-gradient(to right, #1a2a6c, #204a87);
--primary-button: #1976d2;
--primary-button-hover: #7a68a6;
--fiv-color: #1976d2;
}
body {
font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
margin: 0;
padding: 0;
font-size: 11px;
color: var(--text-primary);
line-height: 1.6;
background-color: var(--background);
}
.invoice-container {
width: 210mm;
min-height: 297mm;
margin: 0 auto;
background-color: var(--one-color);
box-shadow: var(--card-shadow);
padding: 25mm;
box-sizing: border-box;
}
.invoice-header {
background: var(--header-bg-gradient);
color: var(--one-color);
padding: 20px 25mm;
margin: -25mm -25mm 30px -25mm;
overflow: hidden;
border-bottom: 5px solid var(--fiv-color);
}
.invoice-header .logo-text {
float: left;
font-size: 24px;
font-weight: bold;
margin: 0;
color: var(--two-color);
}
.invoice-header .header-info {
float: right;
text-align: right;
font-size: 11px;
}
.invoice-header .header-info span {
display: block;
margin-bottom: 3px;
}
.invoice-header .header-info strong {
font-weight: bold;
color: var(--one-color);
}
.company-contact {
margin-top: 15px;
text-align: left;
font-size: 10px;
color: var(--two-color);
}
.invoice-title-status {
margin-bottom: 25px;
font-size: 14px;
padding-top: 10px;
}
.invoice-title-status h1 {
float: left;
margin: 0;
color: var(--fiv-color);
font-size: 20px;
}
.invoice-title-status .status-badge {
float: right;
background-color: var(--fiv-color);
color: var(--one-color);
padding: 5px 12px;
border-radius: 20px;
font-size: 12px;
font-weight: bold;
text-transform: uppercase;
}
.invoice-title-status .status-badge.pending { background-color: var(--cambio); }
.invoice-title-status .status-badge.canceled { background-color: #F44336; }
.info-grid {
display: flex;
justify-content: space-between;
margin-bottom: 30px;
gap: 20px;
}
.info-block {
flex: 1;
background-color: var(--two-color);
padding: 10px;
border-radius: 5px;
}
.info-block h3 {
margin: 0;
font-size: 14px;
}
.items-table {
width: 100%;
border-collapse: collapse;
margin-bottom: 30px;
}
.items-table th, .items-table td {
border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
padding: 8px;
text-align: left;
}
.items-table th {
background-color: var(--three-color);
}
.total {
font-size: 16px;
font-weight: bold;
text-align: right;
margin-top: 20px;
}
</style>
<div class="invoice-container">
<div class="invoice-header">
ColproMarket
<span>Fecha: <%= invoice.date %><span>Factura #: <%= invoice._id %><div class="invoice-title-status">
FacturaPagado
<div class="info-block">
Cliente<%= invoice.client.name %><%= invoice.client.address %><%= invoice.client.phone %>
Detalles de Envío<%= invoice.shipping.address %><%= invoice.shipping.city %><%= invoice.shipping.zip %>
<thead>
<tr>
<th>Descripción<th>Cantidad<th>Precio Unitario<th>Total<tbody>
<% invoice.items.forEach(function(item) { %>
<tr>
<td><%= item.description %><td><%= item.quantity %><td><%= item.unitPrice.toFixed(2) %>€<td><%= (item.quantity * item.unitPrice).toFixed(2) %>€<% }) %>
<div class="total">
Total: <%= invoice.total.toFixed(2) %>€